name: RTCConfiguration.iceTransportPolicy
description: The WebRTC Device API dictionary RTCConfiguration's iceTransportPolicy property is a string indicating the transport selection policy the ICE agent should use during negotiation of connections. Its value must come from the RTCIceTransportPolicy enumerated type.
